# Added 2026-04-20 — catch common secret filename patterns (three incidents in one session)
Anthropic-Key
**/Anthropic-Key
**/*-Key
**/*-Token
**/*-PAT
**/*-Secret

# Catch keys/tokens anywhere in basename (file 'Claude Key-Open-Router'
# slipped past *-Key/*-Token because it doesn't end with those suffixes).
**/*[Kk]ey*
**/*[Tt]oken*
**/*[Ss]ecret*
**/*[Cc]redential*
!**/node_modules/**
